<p><strong>Commentary:</strong> SPC-507 was my 1st GOI Format, written in May 2018, and my 1st entry in the 2018 Doomsday Contest.</p>
<p>One thing I wasn't too happy about was the page's density, which people had heavily criticized at the time. After receiving a large amount of critique and spending time rewriting significant portions of this, I'm now proud to say it: This should be an enjoyable read!</p>
<p>Either way, this was my attempt at giving the Centre a reason to exist in the main Foundation Universe. It also gives the Avian Division more power to fight that devious Thoth!</p>
<p>I plan on writing more SPC in the future.</p>
